# $Gateweaver: TODO,v 1.1 2006/01/04 02:51:35 cmaxwell Exp $

Some random ideas that might be useful to implement.

- no cash-out on credit card items
- multiple menu item names: display, customer, kitchen
- order editing
- print modules
  currently prints a 2-column receipt using epson codes.  Allow changing to
  paginated, single page, etc.
- dual-station print
  print customer receipt at counter, kitchen ticket in kitchen
- time-shifted printing
  allow orders to be delayed for later processing
- credit card / debit processing
- cash accounting
- gift cards / coupons
- reporting:
	- daily, weekly, monthly, yearly sales
	- time-of-day sales
	- item usage
